\fs36 Menus  \

\fs16 \
\

\pard\tx2620\tx3120\tx3620\b0\fs28\li2100 Menus give the user access to the full breadth of an application's functionality.  A user should be able to get a good idea of what an application does by looking at its menu commands.  The application's menu commands are grouped into menus, as shown below.\

